Package project3

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Company
    The Company class stores a grab bag container of employees and performs payroll operations.
    Date
    Date is a class that stores the day, month, and year, used mainly for the hiring date of an employee.
    Employee
    Employee is a class to store the profile of an employee, and their period earnings.
    Fulltime
    Fulltime class is an extension of the Employee class.
    Management
    Management class is an extension of the Fulltime class.
    Parttime
    Parttime class is an extension of the Employee class.
    Profile
    Profile is a class to store an employees personal information that is contained within the Employee class.
